        </item>
        <item>
            <title>西九 13 个价值 20 万 CPU 被窃，外媒：很可能是 Threadripper 2990WX 或 Intel 18 核心 Core i9-9980XE</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/31/13-cpu/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=13-cpu</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/31/13-cpu/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[EMMA]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 31 Oct 2023 10:06:10 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技趣闻]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1202309</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>西九文化区昨日前发生爆窃案，其办公室内 13 部电脑的中央处理器（CPU）及 1 部 iPad 被盗。</p><p>警方于昨日（30 日）上午 9 时接获西九文化区办公室职员报案，指其返回办公室上班时，发现办公室内 13 部电脑的中央处理器（CPU）被及 1 部平板电脑 iPad 盗取。</p><p>警员接报到场后调查发现，办公室有一扇铝窗被撬毁，疑盗贼撬窗潜入爆窃。警方现正深入调查案件，追缉贼人归案。</p><p>据了解，仅电脑内部的 CPU 处理器被拆走，盗贼并无偷走整部电脑。而办公室职员称这批电脑于 2018 年购入，当时每部售价超过＄ 4 万港元，而所有被窃 CPU 价值合共约＄20 万港币。</p><p>资讯科技网站 Tom&#8217;s Hardware 对此事表示，经翻查 2018 年的 CPU 规格，当时要价接近 1.5 万港元的 CPU 有 AMD 32 核心的 Ryzen Threadripper 2990WX 以及 Intel 18 核心 Core i9-9980XE，而西九办公室内的 CPU 很可能是上述其中一款。</p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.tomshardware.com/news/thieves-remove-cpus-from-13-pcs-at-hong-kong-government-office">tomshardware</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div></p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/31/13-cpu/fun-tech/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>加拿大禁政府装置用 WeChat    同时禁用俄国卡巴斯基产品</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/31/wechat-6/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=wechat-6</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/31/wechat-6/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[毛]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 31 Oct 2023 08:30:31 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[城中热话]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技趣闻]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[wechat]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[加拿大]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[卡巴斯基]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1202312</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>加拿大政府昨（30 日）宣布，禁止用户在政府的流动装置上使用内地的通讯应用程式 WeChat 及俄罗斯的防毒程式卡巴斯基。</p><p>两款应用程式将于下周一起从政府的行动装置中删除，用户亦无法再度重新下载。而加拿大今年二月亦在政府设备上禁止用户使用 Tik Tok。</p><p>加拿大财政部首席资讯长认为，腾讯旗下的微信及总部位于莫斯科的卡巴斯基的应用程式「对私隐和安全造成了不可接受的风险」，故宣布上述的禁令。他亦强调，加拿大政府的资讯并未收到损害，</p><p>俄罗斯的防毒程式卡巴斯基回应指，加拿大在下决定前并无对公司在出作出任何警告。卡巴斯基认为本次的行动是对地缘政治气候的反应，而非因应卡巴斯基产品的评估，表示对加拿大政府的行动感到惊讶及失望。</p><p>有媒体向 WeChat 寻求回应，但 WeChat 在截稿前并未回应置评要求。</p><p>而美国的财政部门表示，虽然现时没有证据显示政府资料被泄露，但应用程式大量收集设备内的资料，认为使用该两款应用程式的风险是「显而易见」。</p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.reuters.com/technology/canada-bans-wechat-kaspersky-applications-government-devices-statement-2023-10-30/">Reuters</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div></p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/31/wechat-6/fun-tech/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>Apple「Scary Fast」30 分钟发布会，由 iPhone 15 Pro Max 拍摄 + Mac 剪片</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/31/apple-scary-fastiphone-15-pro-max/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=apple-scary-fastiphone-15-pro-max</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/31/apple-scary-fastiphone-15-pro-max/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[EMMA]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 31 Oct 2023 08:12:36 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技趣闻]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1202275</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Apple 早前举行约 30 分钟的「Scary Fast」发布会，其中发表配备 M3 系列晶片的 MacBook Pro 等产品。不过更另人惊讶的是，全程发表会是利用 iPhone 15 Pro Max 拍摄。</p><p>在活动影片中，Apple 展示了配备全新的 M3、M3 Pro 和 M3 Max 晶片系列的 14 及 16 吋 MacBook Pro、全新太空黑色 MBP 和 24 吋 iMac。</p><p>而在影片的最后，Apple CEO Timothy Cook 向观众表示感谢后，便出现了「发表会摄自 iPhone 并在 Mac 上剪辑」的字眼，并指所有发表者、地点和无人机画面都是使用 iPhone 15 Pro Max 拍摄。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Apple-Event-October-30-8-16-screenshot.png"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1202320" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Apple-Event-October-30-8-16-screenshot-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Apple-Event-October-30-8-16-screenshot-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Apple-Event-October-30-8-16-screenshot-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Apple-Event-October-30-8-16-screenshot-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Apple-Event-October-30-8-16-screenshot-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Apple-Event-October-30-8-16-screenshot.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Apple-Event-October-30-2-47-screenshot.png"><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1202319" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Apple-Event-October-30-2-47-screenshot-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Apple-Event-October-30-2-47-screenshot-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Apple-Event-October-30-2-47-screenshot-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Apple-Event-October-30-2-47-screenshot-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Apple-Event-October-30-2-47-screenshot-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Apple-Event-October-30-2-47-screenshot.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1202295" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-31-14.00.34-694x376.png" alt="" width="694" height="376" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-31-14.00.34-694x376.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-31-14.00.34-1280x693.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-31-14.00.34-768x416.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-31-14.00.34-1536x832.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-31-14.00.34.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Apple 过去一直指 iPhone 拍摄的影片可达荷里活电影等级，而此影片为可谓绝佳的宣传和证明手法。此外，iPhone 15 Pro 支援 ProRes 格式，如果连接外部储存装置，能以 4K/60 fps 录影，而 iPhone 15 Pro 也是市面上第一部支援色彩流程 ACES（Academy Color Encoding System）的手机。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_52956"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ctkW3V0Mh-k?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;controls=1&#038;color=white&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;rel=0&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.benzinga.com/news/23/10/35504880/apples-not-so-tiny-flex-cupertino-shoots-halloween-themed-scary-fast-event-on-iphone-15-pro-max">benzinga</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div></p>
]]>
