        <item>
            <title>仁孚引入两款全新 smart #1 电动车，预计 2024 年首季可正式交付</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/31/benz-smart1/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=benz-smart1</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/31/benz-smart1/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[EMMA]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 31 Oct 2023 05:57:26 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[车坛动向]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[benz]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[EV]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Mercedes]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[smart]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1202246</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>由中国吉利控股及德国 Mercedes-Benz 集团合资经营的迷你车和微型车系列品牌 smart 近日在港举行盛大的发布会。由仁孚行担任港澳地区的 <span lang="EN-US">smar<wbr />t </span>总经销商，宣布率先在港澳市场接受订购的首款全新纯电型号「smart #1」系列，首批发售版本包括「smart #1 BRABUS」以及「smart #1 Premium」，预计将于 2024 年首季正式交付。</p><p>Smart 表示，与高性能车制造商 BRABUS 联乘推出的高性能版「smart #1 BRABU」，配备前后合共两组高性能摩打，具 428 匹强大马力及 543Nm 峰值扭力，静止加速至时速 100 公里只需 3.9 秒，新车亦配合 AWD 全时四驱系统、跑车化底盘及悬挂系统。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1202265" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/JAN06975-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/JAN06975-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/JAN06975-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/JAN06975-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/JAN06975-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/JAN06975-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1202266" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/JAN07108-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/JAN07108-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/JAN07108-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/JAN07108-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/JAN07108-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/JAN07108-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1202267" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2630-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2630-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2630-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2630-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2630-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2630-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1202268" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2655-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2655-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2655-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2655-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2655-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2655-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1202269" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2677-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2677-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2677-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2677-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2677-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2677-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>公司又指，smart #1 BRABUS 亦提供多种预设驾驶模式，例如选择节能为主的 ECO 后驱模式，在 WLTP 模式下的最长续航距离便提升至 400 公里。</p><p>「smart #1 BRABUS」车身配备专属的车体扰流组件，例如前、后包围、车侧裙脚及车顶尾翼、又有 19 吋 Dynamo 合金轮圈及鲜红色涂层制动卡钳。车厢内则以 Alcantara 物料覆盖外层的三幅式軚环、跑车式加速及制动脚踏板、配色对比强烈的 BRABUS 跑车桶型座椅、像真程度极高的模拟引擎音效系统，以及由音响品牌 Beats Audio 专责主理及设定的 13 声道高级音响。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1202271 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2736-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2736-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2736-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2736-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2736-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2736-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1202270 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2735-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2735-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2735-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2735-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2735-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2735-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>采用全新设计风格的「smart #1 Premium」车头及车尾配备 CyberSparks+智能 LED 头灯、19 吋合金轮圈、Portal Door 新型车门、「Halo roof」天幕式玻璃车顶。车身长阔高为 4,270×1,822×1,636mm，轴距达 2,750mm，车内空间非常宽敞，而悬浮式车顶及车身设有多种色调配搭，可供车主根据个人喜好自订组合。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1202248" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/JAN06925-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/JAN06925-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/JAN06925-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/JAN06925-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/JAN06925-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/JAN06925-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1202259" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2682-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2682-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2682-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2682-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2682-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2682-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" />  <img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1202261" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2688-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2688-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2688-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2688-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2688-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2688-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1202262" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2703-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2703-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2703-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2703-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2703-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2703-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>而车内的前座可作 6 方位电动调校，采用全车多媒体及辅助系统操作中枢的 12.8 吋轻触式大型 LED 显示荧幕、Beats 13 声道扬声器系统，以及对应 Apple Carplay 和 Android Auto。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1202263 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2704-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2704-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2704-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2704-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2704-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/MI3_2704-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1202250 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/JAN06942-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/JAN06942-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/JAN06942-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/JAN06942-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/JAN06942-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/JAN06942-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: left;">「smart #1 Premium」采用 RWD 后轮驱动设计，具 272 匹马力及 343Nm 峰值扭力，在静止加速至时速 100 公里下需 6.7 秒，WLTP 模式下有长达 440 公里的最长续航距，足以应付日常用车需要。另外，smart 亦将车侧睹后镜盲点侦测显示（BSD）、车前（FCTA）及车后（RCTA）横越预警系统、 行车线辅助系统（LKA）、360 度鸟瞰式监察镜头、设有自动停车及开行功能的主动巡航系统 （ACC）、自动泊车辅助系统（APA）等主被动行车安全数码系统加入新车中。</p><p><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1202247 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/JAN06921-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/JAN06921-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/JAN06921-1280x853.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/JAN06921-768x512.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/JAN06921-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/JAN06921-scaled.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>两款 smart #1 型号于 11 月 1 日起在 smart showroon 举行优先预览，有兴趣者可于网上预约参观。另外，全新的 smart 香港官方网页（hk.smart.com）亦同时开于，接收买家于网上预订及创造个人化「smart #1」。</p><p>首批「smart #1 BRABUS」及「smart #1 Premium」买家可享早鸟优惠预订新车，售价分别由 HK$339,000 及$299,000 起。首批新车将于 2024 年第一季正式交付，以配合明年 3 月底届满的电动车「一换一」首次登记税宽减安排。</p><p>资料来源：smart</p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div></p>
]]>
